OL,3,CCosmic Kiss: Exact time to see rare
OL,4,Cmoment planets come together in night
OL,5,Csky
OL,7,FThe next few nights are the peak time
OL,8,Fto see an unusual astronomical
OL,9,Fphenomenon - a Cosmic Kiss.
OL,11,FIt will be quite a rare view in the
OL,12,Fnight sky for those captivated by
OL,13,Fstargazing and planetary activity.
OL,15,FBut when exactly is the best time to
OL,16,Fspot it?
OL,18,FWhat is a Cosmic Kiss?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
